## 阅读如下代码，写出代码的功能，输入和输出
```js
Vue.filter('toThousandFilter', function(num){
  return (+num || 0).toString().replace(/^-?\d+/g, m => m.replace(/(?=(?!\b)(\d{3})+$)/g, ','))
});
```
